            <div class="top-image-area__header">
                <div class="header_inner_content">
                    <h1 class="home-header-with-drop">Career support</h1>

                        <p class="home-header-with-drop">
We offer support for members at every career stage. Whether you're just starting out or approaching retirement, we’re here to help. 
</p>
                </div>
                <div class="top-image-area__cta">

                        <a class="cta__link cta--yellow click-ripple" href="/careers/cpd/practising-scientists/">
