<h3><a href="/careers/job-seeking/"><strong>Job seeking</strong></a></h3>
<p>We can help you discover your next role &ndash; and equip you with the confidence and skills to prepare for your application. Using our advice, make your CV stand out and ensure a strong interview.</p>
<h4>Who is it for?</h4>
<p>Anyone looking for their next role.</p>
<p><strong>✓ Royal Society of Chemistry membership (any category)</strong></p>
