<p>Wondering what to do with your chemistry degree, or taking your career in a new direction? We have case studies showcasing the career pathways and journeys of other chemical scientists to help you plan your career.</p>
<h4>Who is it for?</h4>
<p>Everyone especially chemical scientists looking to take the next step in their career whether that&rsquo;s a role or some professional development.</p>
<p><strong>✓ Royal Society of Chemistry membership (any category)</strong></p>
